<i>noun</i>: 서문 [서ː문], 머리말 [머리말], 권두 [권두] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>서문 [서ː문]</dt><br>
<dd>preface; foreword; introduction</dd><br>
<dd>책이나 글의 첫 부분에 내용이나 목적 등을 간단하게 적은 글.</dd><br>
<dd>The front part of a book or piece of writing with a simple description of its content, purpose, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>머리말 [머리말]</dt><br>
<dd>preface</dd><br>
<dd>책이나 글의 첫 부분에 내용이나 목적 등을 간단하게 적은 글.</dd><br>
<dd>A short introduction at the beginning of a book or a written piece, informing the readers of its contents or purpose.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>권두 [권두]</dt><br>
<dd>preface</dd><br>
<dd>책의 첫머리.</dd><br>
<dd>The introduction of a book.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>